			<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-07-16T11:36:00-07:00" itemprop="datePublished"><a href="https://blog.sucuri.net/2016/04/website-ransomware-ctb-locker-goes-blockchain.html#comment-7774">July 16, 2016</a></time></p>		</header>

