 feel their pain. I want to see these evil bad people in court. I want<br />
them to know that they have HURT PEOPLE and I want to see them go away<br />
for the rest of their lives.</p>
<p>I want to thank Roxy Lopez again for her courage in taking on this<br />
global issue and I thank here again for her time. Hopefully together we<br />
can get this very serious issue into a greater light and maybe the bad<br />
guys will have less places to hide.</p>
<p>Sincerely</p>
<p>Scott Matthew Smith</p>
